Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.77,0:00:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,前情提要
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.60,0:00:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好嗆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.40,0:00:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,這是當然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.98,0:00:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,如果願望能實現就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.69,0:00:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我想趕快洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.24,0:00:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,給我安靜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.74,0:00:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Good
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.78,0:00:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,哈哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.28,0:00:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.95,0:00:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.70,0:00:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕了 零食袋空了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.42,0:00:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 還零食袋咧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.58,0:00:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,肚子餓了會很傷腦筋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.88,0:00:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,到晚餐前還有點時間呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.01,0:00:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,在前面正好有間超市喔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.09,0:00:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,大叔 稍微繞一下路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.43,0:00:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.72,0:00:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 買了好多
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.35,0:00:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,一下買這麼多是要怎樣啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.02,0:00:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那個有備什麼的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.77,0:00:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Good
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.61,0:00:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Good個頭啦
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.29,0:01:09.50,OP - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}ナゾナゾみたいな恋してみるかい？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.50,0:01:12.05,OP - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}星が囁く
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.17,0:01:14.97,OP - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}怖いけど…ありかな！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.47,0:01:20.43,OP - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}なんとなく生きてる　なんてつまらない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.60,0:01:25.18,OP - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}本当は何かを変えてみたいのです
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.18,0:01:28.90,OP - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}きっかけが欲しいから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.06,0:01:30.57,OP - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}飛んで飛んでBoooon！！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.57,0:01:34.74,OP - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}思い出が騒いでる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.74,0:01:40.33,OP - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}私…あなたを知ってるみたい！？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.70,0:01:44.45,OP - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}晴れても雨でも雪の日でも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.45,0:01:47.21,OP - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}会いに会いに行っちゃいたい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.42,0:01:48.62,OP - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}ムカシ→ミライ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.75,0:01:49.88,OP - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}アシタ→ミライ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.04,0:01:52.75,OP - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}そうだね　時はNonstop
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.96,0:01:58.55,OP - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}ちょっと前に悩んでたこと　みんなみんな消しちゃって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.72,0:02:04.43,OP - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}新しい物語　始めましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.60,0:02:09.52,OP - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}また夢見てる？いまの夢はまだ秘密！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.02,0:02:12.36,OP - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}晴れ晴れよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.86,0:02:15.03,OP - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}降れ降れよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.19,0:02:20.11,OP - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}どんな天気だって I need you！！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.29,0:01:09.50,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}想試著談場猜謎般的戀愛嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.50,0:01:12.05,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}星星在呢喃著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.17,0:01:14.97,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}雖然害怕…但還是想！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.47,0:01:20.43,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}光是安穩度日 也太無趣了點
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.60,0:01:25.18,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}真希望能改變些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.18,0:01:28.90,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}既然想要個契機
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.06,0:01:30.57,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}那就飛奔出去吧 Boooon!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.57,0:01:34.74,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}回憶在騷動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.74,0:01:40.33,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}我…好像認識你！？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.70,0:01:44.45,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}不論是晴天雨天還是在下雪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.45,0:01:47.21,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}我都好想好想去見你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.42,0:01:48.62,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}從過去到未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.75,0:01:49.88,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}從明天到未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.04,0:01:52.75,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}是啊 時間 Nonstop
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.96,0:01:58.55,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}先前煩惱的事情 通通都消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.72,0:02:04.43,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}來展開新的故事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.60,0:02:09.52,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}又在做夢嗎？現在的夢還不能說！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.02,0:02:12.36,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}大晴天也好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.86,0:02:15.03,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}下雨天也好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.19,0:02:20.11,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}不管是怎樣的天氣 I need you!!
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
